{"tid":2385599,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食肉獸是靚午","createTime":"2021-01-29T06:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T12:03:18.000Z","uid":123401,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46b6d98b088396e5eb1a76a8212ad0c4715ff77c","tid":2385599,"uid":123401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ph8f2XB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPh8f2XB.png&h=3fa81612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肉燥炸脾飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未上菜，先評服務。<br />\n一開始叫左多汁，本身只係想多d汁撈飯，不過個侍應問我係咪想多醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ndiu，窮撚既心思比佢睇穿左。最尾上到黎，又真係幾多肉燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n檯底個櫃d餐具調味料都好足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFAaRTu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFAaRTu.png&h=a371a2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再評下餐飯<br />\n肉燥：夠香夠味，油量適中，份量好足，淨係肉燥就夠送曬成碗飯。同埋驚喜位係入面仲有d細細舊豬軟骨，咬落幾有層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞脾：雖然menu話係巨人雞脾，我覺得size 就正常，但對比起其他鋪，都算多肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞脾皮炸得好脆，醃得入味，大部分d肉都算淋，唔柴，但如果炸少30s 應該更加香嫩多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鹵水蛋（仲有半粒係雞脾下面）：扣分位，切得有d 樣衰，同埋唔入味<br />\n<br />\n奶茶：甜度應該做左d調整，無特別要少甜但飲落係其他茶記既少甜level，茶味香濃而不苦澀，幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，個餐仲跟例湯（太多野好full，真係飲唔落）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總體黎講，真係幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />掛住台灣了"},{"pid":"172bfdec1234e35b6bb43a5e1834da623c479eeb","tid":2385599,"uid":361777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbaca1cdf17014f24304632fdbf227858b1874b0","tid":2385599,"uid":123401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"172bfdec1234e35b6bb43a5e1834da623c479eeb","tid":2385599,"uid":361777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:38:15.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}